{"title":"deepin系统安装后检测不到声卡，无声音","slug":"deepin_1","date":"2020-10-10T12:01:00.000Z","updated":"2021-09-10T16:16:05.244Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/deepin_1.json","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"1-准备工作\"><a href=\"#1-准备工作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.准备工作\"></a>1.准备工作</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1.检查电脑是否能够检测到声卡的输入输出</span><br><span class=\"line\">方法：设置里面-声音-高级设置-看是否有输出输入设备</span><br><span class=\"line\">2.确认声卡是否出现物理损坏导致的物理信息无法被系统读取</span><br><span class=\"line\">代码指令：</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo lspci | grep audio </span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo lspci -v</span><br><span class=\"line\">看是否有类似的声卡反馈</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"2-修改grub文件内容\"><a href=\"#2-修改grub文件内容\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.修改grub文件内容\"></a>2.修改grub文件内容</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1.修改grub文件里面的文件  添加一个指令即可</span><br><span class=\"line\">GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT&#x3D;&quot;$&#123;这里你的原有配置不要动&#125; snd_hda_intel.dmic_detect&#x3D;0&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">指令如下：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#进入root模式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">su </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> /etc/default/</span><br><span class=\"line\">vi grub</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 将此代码snd_hda_intel.dmic_detect=0 加入grub即可</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 1.按键盘i 进入插入模式，修改添加代码后</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#2.【esc】然后 按【：】输入 【w！】</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">reboot <span class=\"comment\">#重启即可</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"3-分享一下我的公众号和小程序\"><a href=\"#3-分享一下我的公众号和小程序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.分享一下我的公众号和小程序\"></a>3.分享一下我的公众号和小程序</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">不定时更新哦！</span><br><span class=\"line\">感谢关注</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>如有疑问联系客服，小程序即可直接联系</li>\n<li>禁止转载，严禁商用，如若转载标明来源</li>\n</ul>\n","more":"<h2 id=\"1-准备工作\"><a href=\"#1-准备工作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.准备工作\"></a>1.准备工作</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1.检查电脑是否能够检测到声卡的输入输出</span><br><span class=\"line\">方法：设置里面-声音-高级设置-看是否有输出输入设备</span><br><span class=\"line\">2.确认声卡是否出现物理损坏导致的物理信息无法被系统读取</span><br><span class=\"line\">代码指令：</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo lspci | grep audio </span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo lspci -v</span><br><span class=\"line\">看是否有类似的声卡反馈</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"2-修改grub文件内容\"><a href=\"#2-修改grub文件内容\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.修改grub文件内容\"></a>2.修改gru